The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Good Morning

 Hello It's Monday, October 18, 2004

 Road to avoid

 SP Mukherjee Road. One flank closed to lay water pipeline.

 Interface

 An interactive session with Shankersinh Vaghela, minister of textiles, government of India, hosted by Merchants? Chamber of Commerce, at The Park, 5 pm.

 Contest

 A water-colour painting competition and exhibition at Bharatiyam, 3 pm to 8 pm.

 Navratri

 Dandiya, live Gujarati music, food and shopping at Navratri Mahotsav, at The Stadel, 8 pm onwards. 

 Exhibition

 Art in Life, an exhibition of brassware, garments, jewellery and artefacts at CIMA Gallery, 11 am to 8 pm.

 An exhibition of books, photographs on sports of Russia at Gorky Sadan.

 Paintings, sketches, gift items and cards on view at Gaganendra Pradarshashala, 3 pm.

 Art watch

 Devi, an exhibition of paintings, on view at Chitrakoot Art Gallery, 3 pm to 8 pm.




